issuer.label: IdP Issuer
issuer.description: Also known as the IdP Entity ID. This is a unique string that identifies the IdP.

userIdProfileField.label: User ID Profile Field
userIdProfileField.description: Select the profile field in your data store that contains your users' IDs.

spLoginUrl.label: Blackboard Learn Login URL
spLoginUrl.tooltip: The URL for your users to log into your Blackboard Learn instance.

assertionValidHours.tooltip: This is the time period in which a SAML Assertion is valid. It is referred to as "SAML Not After" in the SAML Specification.

assertionOffsetMinutes.tooltip: This is referred to as "SAML Not Before" in the SAML Specification.
